www.youtube.com/embed/zTIJAgTai40","width":1280,"height":720},"title":{"simpleText":"YEAR"},"description":{"simpleText":"YEAR: The ASL sign for \"year\" has two common versions:\n1. A longer version in which the dominant hand travels all the way around the non-dominant hand. See: https://youtu.be/zTIJAgTai40\n\n2. A more abbreviated \"advanced\" version of \"year\" in which the dominant hand makes a small forward rotation movement above the non-dominant hand.  \nSee:  https://youtu.be/jw_R6ttIrgg American Sign Language - ASL  \nLearn sign language at https://www.Lifeprint.com\nDonations appreciated (to help pay for hosting and related expenses). Please help:   \nhttps://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick\u0026hosted_button_id=64QMBRBXQSV6G\nThanks!\nOr, if you prefer \"Cash App\" you can use: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/bookstore.htm\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see: https://www.youtube.com/billvicars\nTo learn basic fingerspelling see https://youtu.be/va1aAXpVr2w\n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages-layout/instructor.htm\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\n- Dr. Bill\n:)"},"lengthSeconds":"4","ownerProfileUrl":"http://www.youtube.com/@aslu","externalChannelId":"UCZy9xs6Tn9vWqN_5l0EEIZA","isFamilySafe":true,"availableCountries":["AD","AE","AF","AG","AI","AL","AM","AO","AQ","AR","AS","AT","AU","AW","AX","AZ","BA","BB","BD","BE","BF","BG","BH","BI","BJ","BL","BM","BN","BO","BQ","BR","BS","BT","BV","BW","BY","BZ","CA","CC","CD","CF","CG","CH","CI","CK","CL","CM","CN","CO","CR","CU","CV","CW","CX","CY","CZ","DE","DJ","DK","DM","DO","DZ","EC","EE","EG","EH","ER","ES","ET","FI","FJ","FK","FM","FO","FR","GA","GB","GD","GE","GF","GG","GH","GI","GL","GM","GN","GP","GQ","GR","GS","GT","GU","GW","GY","HK","HM","